helpers/README.md-6- - `quickshell-update-installer` — shares the checker lock, restores the previous lockfile when `nh os switch` fails, writes the native cache schema and refreshes Quickshell over IPC.
helpers/README.md-7- - `quickshell-system-stats` — persistent Python telemetry process reading `/proc`, `statvfs` and backlight sysfs directly without per-second shell subprocesses.
helpers/README.md-8- - `quickshell-gpu-monitor` — zero-copy wrapper around the upstream streaming GPU monitor with the NVIDIA library path set once outside QML.
